{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-initials/task-25","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Slušao sam zvuk i vežbavao izgovor početnih glasova i slogova.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"zh-a1-learn-initials","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Zvuk <span class=\"highlighted-text\">k</span> izgovara se zadnjim delom jezika protiv mekanog nepca, slično kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">g</span>. Ali za razliku od <span class=\"highlighted-text\">g</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">k</span> se izgovara jačim dahanjem. To omogućava jak izliv vazduha.</p>\n<p>Pokušaj da izgovoriš <span class=\"highlighted-text\">k</span> kao da te snažan udarac vazduha pogađa po ruci ako staviš ruku ispred usta. Zatim, pokušaj sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">g</span> i trebalo bi da osetiš gotovo nedostatak vazduha.</p>\n<p>Kada <span class=\"highlighted-text\">k</span> se kombinuje sa završetkom <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">e</span>, i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span>, dobija slogove: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ka</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ke</span>, i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ku</span>.</p>\n<p>Da vežbamo izgovor ovih slogova, zatim koristi <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ke</span> u različitim tonovima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Herufi</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">kē</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">稞</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">ké</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">咳</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">kě</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">可</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">kè</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">刻</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-initials/task-25"},"questions":[],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company3-reception.png","characters":[{"character":"Wang Hua","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ZH_A1_pinyin_initials.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":410.22,"finishTimestamp":427.86},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":1.52,"dialogue":{"text":"k","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":2.72,"finishTime":3.32,"dialogue":{"text":"ka","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":4.66,"finishTime":5.34,"dialogue":{"text":"ke","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":7.06,"finishTime":7.75,"dialogue":{"text":"ku","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":9.42,"finishTime":10.32,"dialogue":{"text":"kē","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":12.43,"finishTime":13.37,"dialogue":{"text":"ké","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":14.93,"finishTime":15.94,"dialogue":{"text":"kě","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":17.63,"finishTime":18.24,"dialogue":{"text":"kè","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":18.74,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"sup